<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to Scribe!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      color: #666;
    }
    a {
      color: #1a73e8;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome to Scribe!</h1>
  <p>Thank you for downloading Scribe! We're thrilled to have you with us. With Scribe, your creativity is about to get a major boost. Our AI-powered app is designed to help you generate captivating titles and optimize your content effortlessly.</p>
  <p>Dive right in and start creating by visiting your <a href="<%= @url %>">Scribe Dashboard</a>. Let's take your content to the next level!</p>
  <p>Your Login Credentials:</p> 
  <p>Email: <%= @email %></p>
  <p>Password: <%= @password %></p>
  <p>Happy Scribbling!</p>
  <p>Best,<br>The Scribe Team</p>
</body>
</html>
